   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Sustainable Development for Nali School in Ghana</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Cheerful Hearts Foundation plans to develop Nali International School to assist the poorest families in the community. Initial project is to construct fresh access to sanitary drinking water. We also aim to reconstruct the toilet facilities as current ones are near collapse &amp; the leaking sewage is risking the children&apos;s health. We seek sustainable resources development with investment in textbooks and learning aids so that children can borrow &amp; prevent financial burden keeping them out of school</narrative>
  </description>
